---
title: Salsa-Topped Pork Chops with Jewelled Rice and Crispy Tortilla Topping
description: Chips for dinner?! We say 'yes'! Our Enchilada Spice Blend brings toasty tortilla chips to the next level and creates a crunchy garnish for this pork and rice dish. Rice dotted with peppers and corn is topped with pork chops smothered in mild salsa.
